{"tid":2446144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"手足唔能夠再情緒用事，大家只得  表忠 / 離開  兩條路你揀。","createTime":"2021-03-14T08:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T02:00:23.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0b214ab38bbf932b659b62b6b99c124639c29e","tid":2446144,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"依家你間屋俾人入侵左，佢有槍有炮你乜都冇，自然唔夠佢揪。 如果你唔憤氣衝動下繼續打，個下場就係你死先。而理性去取捨只得兩個選擇 一表忠奶 二執包袱離開。<br />\n<br />\n依家你需要有所計算，如果你真係好嬲，認為做人要講真話要有尊嚴重要過少少經濟利益等等，可以為咗講真話而重新嚟過都得嘅，咁請你選擇第二方案。 相反如果你覺得錢先係最重要，又或者幾十歲人好難再闖，又有家爺仔乸要養，咁可能第一選擇先係岩你，但係就要放棄講真話自由嘅權利。<br />\n<br />\n而如果你係後生而冇錢，係可以留港賺錢鬆人，正所謂「香港精神，搵錢走人！」。相反話要留低繼續頂既，亦都唔好睇到自己咁強，因為都是去到唔表忠就冇飯開嘅，我相信你都唔頂得好耐。 到時你餓死左我最多講幾句尊敬你嘅說話。<br />\n<br />\n大家必須要學識唔好情緒用事，唔憤氣嗰啲乜都係假。因為如果做人下下為啖氣而做，通常都奶野，依家奶野係要坐監的。 一同二呢個係一個好現實嘅抉擇，現實係冇得討論接唔接受，而係擺在眼前必須要面對。"},{"pid":"ae5f6388c8213cd5204b8cea3a0cf8df58bbc5e2","tid":2446144,"uid":114193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"做順民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為連下sir 忠實信徒<br />\n堅決支持連下sir 信念：<br />\n反黑暴，保政權，黃屍港毒一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我copy連下sir 每日嘅大作你哋睇<br />\n震懾下你班連登黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大DQ學生會一事足以證明只能放棄香港，留底只能夠選擇表忠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423210</a><br />\n<br />\n「安心出行」根本就冇得避，留底既香港人只會能夠接受～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2401117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2401117</a><br />\n<br />\n依家講到明連選舉都唔俾你玩，請問啲留港抗爭撚點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417881</a><br />\n<br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ed1532f499826e630e102e9214a58c40035c439e","tid":2446144,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲係人性嘅陰暗面，每個人背後都有所計算<br />\n我亦都好相信嗰200幾個唔肯宣誓效忠嘅公務員，佢一定有後路唔使餓死先走，如果唔係佢一定會簽。<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係現實。依家係生存戰並不是什麼抗爭。<br />\n你可以繼續老屈我叫人做順民，但係你老屈我之前你心中已經有所答案。我相信你自己都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b6d083de900071a6f830769654ce17ac79e107","tid":2446144,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0ff4d0e3c802c7e3435759886335a49222f9a1","tid":2446144,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c55af63f765fae3864edcf2b6f155b18596084c","tid":2446144,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"人地坐哂監你先黎講呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff5efadd08614e3a2415d06ba458734ca71d2d6","tid":2446144,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"連下sir 日日打長文叫人「表忠」（請自行起底）<br />\n咪即係叫你班黑暴投降做順民囉<br />\n<br />\n同埋連下sir咁多時間資源出咁多政治post <br />\n叫人唔好理政治<br />\n（eg <br />\n［新任務］要學識唔能夠再俾新聞影響到自己情緒！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2432822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2432822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n其他請再自行起底）<br />\n<br />\n就一定係藍絲大台<br />\n<br />\n作為黃轉藍嘅我<br />\n見連下sir 咁多咁inspiring 嘅好文沉落大海<br />\n諗住俾大家重溫下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登黃屍黑暴肆虐<br />\n我哋藍絲陣營沒有分裂嘅本錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p